{"id":"CON","segmentId":"CON","longName":"Consent Segment","description":"This segment identifies patient consent information relating to a particular message.  It can be used as part of existing messages to convey information about patient consent to procedures, admissions, information release/exchange or other events discussed by the message.  It may also be used in messages focusing on recording or requesting consent and for   consents related to employees or service providers.\r\n\r\nThe segment will be used in conjunction with various other segments to identify the practitioner (PRA/STF) or patient (PID) the consent is for, the various individuals involved in the consent (ROL) as witnesses, consenting person (not always the patient), translators, consulting providers, etc., and the specific procedures being proposed (PR1).","sample":"","chapters":["CH_09"],"fields":[{"id":"CON.1","type":"Field","position":"CON.1","name":"Set Id - Con","length":4,"usage":"R","rpt":"1","dataType":"SI","dataTypeName":"Sequence Id","tableId":null,"tableName":null,"description":null,"sample":null,"fields":null},{"id":"CON.2","type":"Field","position":"CON.2","name":"Consent Type","length":0,"usage":"O","rpt":"1","dataType":"CWE","dataTypeName":"Coded With Exceptions","tableId":"0496","tableName":"Consent Type","description":null,"sample":null,"fields":null},{"id":"CON.3","type":"Field","position":"CON.3","name":"Consent Form Id And Version","length":0,"usage":"O","rpt":"1","dataType":"ST","dataTypeName":"String Data","tableId":null,"tableName":null,"description":null,"sample":null,"fields":null},{"id":"CON.4","type":"Field","position":"CON.4","name":"Consent Form Number","length":0,"usage":"O","rpt":"1","dataType":"EI","dataTypeName":"Entity Identifier","tableId":null,"tableName":null,"description":null,"sample":null,"fields":null},{"id":"CON.5","type":"Field","position":"CON.5","name":"Consent Text","length":0,"usage":"O","rpt":"*","dataType":"FT","dataTypeName":"Formatted Text Dat